
** Tags

  <to>me@myself.com</to> is equivalent to 
   to=me@myself.com

** Empty Tag

  *<flag/>* The tag ends by a slash.

** Continuation (same as by Regular Expressions)

  - *
  - ?
  - +

** DTD

  - !DOCTYPE
  - !ELEMENT
  - !ATTLIST

** Attributes

  - CDATA
  - ID
  - IDREF
  - ENTITY or ENTITIES
  - NMTOKEN or NMTOKENS
  - name list


  - # REQUIRED
  - # IMPLIED

  <example>
  <!ATTLIST record 
     id     CDATA #IMPLIED
     name   CDATA #REQUIRED
     age    CDATA #REQUIRED
     stat   (true|false) true
     > 
  </example>

** Comments

  *<!-- This is a comment -->*

